{"tid":597914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京：無意在新任期修憲 不打算2030年再參選","createTime":"2018-03-19T05:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T09:27:02.000Z","uid":3393,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"150a39c19e6fea79685d049ff0a105f2125134e5","tid":597914,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯總統普京表示，現時未有計劃在新的總統任期內，進行任何憲法改革。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，正在考慮政府總理等政府的事宜，一切改變將在就職典禮後宣布。他強調，俄羅斯的政治力量應遵循國家利益，而非集團利益或家族利益，因此必須團結所有人的力量。至於他是否會參加2030年的總統選舉，普京表示，有關猜測可笑，他不打算這樣做。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386547-20180319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386547-20180319.htm&d=fOU4Rf5ouztb7n8%2ByxwvOP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=75845d16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386547-20180319.htm&h=7d25f380\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386547-20180319.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1fa38257c0017d97d2ac0897824a24f756a51bda","tid":597914,"uid":76216,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"150a39c19e6fea79685d049ff0a105f2125134e5","tid":597914,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯總統普京表示，現時未有計劃在新的總統任期內，進行任何憲法改革。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，正在考慮政府總理等政府的事宜，一切改變將在就職典禮後宣布。他強調，俄羅斯的政治力量應遵循國家利益，而非集團利益或家族利益，因此必須團結所有人的力量。至於他是否會參加2030年的總統選舉，普京表示，有關猜測可笑，他不打算這樣做。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386547-20180319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386547-20180319.htm&d=fOU4Rf5ouztb7n8%2ByxwvOP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=75845d16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386547-20180319.htm&h=7d25f380\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386547-20180319.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T05:30:24.000Z